column5: Hey everyone, I am heading out to rice lake this weekend and I was just wondering what is in season right now.  Any panfish in season?  I tried to pull the regs off of the MNR website, but it is running way too slow right now.  Thanks for any help, it is appreciated.
All panfish in season.  perch, sunfish, crappie... enjoy
All the panfish and carp are on season right now.  This weekend will be sunny, so I will suggest you fish a little deeper.
